<br>
1. Show up for raids and show up ontime if humanly possible.<br>
<br>
2. Step up when things go bad such as Devon and Unghure did for us tonight.<br>
<br>
3. Do not miss a Major flag that you need , we cant be held back because 1 person misses a flag.<br>
<br>
4. Regarless of your past look to the future and make a new image by being respectful to the saryrn community and your fellow guildmates.<br>
<br>
We do have a long grueling recruiting period which sucks, but it helps us see what people really wanna be here. We were forced to cut recruits who have missed 4-5 flags thus we are looking to fill 3 spots with hardcore players. <br>
<br>
We now have a great relationship with ToN, Oop, and ToS in regards to assisting each other for flagging purposes and are proud to be working with them.<br>
<br>
We are also seriously looking for a Elemental flagged Beastlord atm as we have no main Bst now.<br>
